Class LowMemorySet<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.Set<T>

    public class LowMemorySet<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.util.AbstractSet<T>
implements java.util.Set<T>
    A set that uses a binary search to find objects in a sorted array. Avoids the memory cost of HashSet, while maintaining reasonable Set.contains(java.lang.Object) Insertions are O(N)!
